body: Great! Thanks for checking. I [pushed](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/commit/e1185bbb4c3fb4331c4523ce8bb97bf46eec6b41) the modified honeybee_honeybee to github. I hope it doesn't happen but you may need to [update honeybee and ladybug](http://hydrashare.github.io/hydra/viewer?owner=mostaphaRoudsari&fork=hydra_1&id=Update_Ladybug_and_Honeybee&slide=0&scale=1&offset=0,0) to avoid version conflicts.
